{"id": "1293150250793697281", "channel_id": "1293150250793697281", "type": 0, "author_id": "1051752197244866681", "author_name": "iceyss_", "author_bot": false, "content": "昨天还骂你们血链的技能小故事没有，今天我又瞅了一眼才发现何止技能小故事啊，背景故事也是直接照搬普通希洛的，这可真是省事完了😅，还有你们照搬都不搬的用心点，希洛的故事二叫希洛，血链就变成赫洛忒了，然后这个赫洛特就是原皮希洛的英文名，但是血链的英文名根本不叫赫洛忒，叫赫洛忒.血链，你们是把原皮英文版的故事拿谷歌翻译翻了一遍贴上来了吗，我是不是还得夸你们勤奋，我求求你们了，你们是觉得你游没有人在乎角色故事和背景吗😅，从之前的繁衍狂热文案量区别对待，到后来的档案馆漏洞百出，再后来艾瑞卡叫N主人的惊世好活，现在希洛这更是演都不演了，做为游戏架构基石之一的角色背景都敷衍成这样你要我怎么相信你们还想好好做游戏😅", "timestamp": "2024-10-08T09:57:25.359000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-10-08T10:46:11.397000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}], "attachments": [{"id": "1293150251091234899", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-08-17-36-21-029_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 202552, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1293150250793697281/1293150251091234899/Screenshot_2024-10-08-17-36-21-029_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a005685&is=69ff0505&hm=681138c1030eb223971dccd01c4ba6b434f6013619297577c6b65df614fb1da9&"}, {"id": "1293150251384967220", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-08-17-36-04-950_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 201442, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1293150250793697281/1293150251384967220/Screenshot_2024-10-08-17-36-04-950_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a005685&is=69ff0505&hm=8b62048818b0967363c67c2245d0aafcd3b407835fe0785f95f2a38f5a475dc5&"}, {"id": "1293150251749998593", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-08-17-46-45-831_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 194050, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1293150250793697281/1293150251749998593/Screenshot_2024-10-08-17-46-45-831_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a005685&is=69ff0505&hm=e757bb315397cbaa9e789f7f7534d602549e17754ce3fbbb73138c3f34062b3c&"}, {"id": "1293150252051726357", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-08-17-36-09-627_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.